h4. Actor:
Customer.

h4. Description:
This is the landing page of Customer's "Disbursed Task" with input form on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* "Disbursement" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click "Disbursed" link.
* Show Landing Page of Customer's "Disbursed Task".

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Disbursed Show Customer Task" privilege.

h4. Process:
* [Get list of Customer's "Disbursed Task"|guide:ExhListUnApprovedTaskForCustomerActionService].

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show list of Customer's "Disbursed Task" in grid view of landing page.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

h4. Related Usecase:
* [Clear Results|common Usecases].
* [List Customer's "Disbursed Task"|guide:ExhListDisbursedTaskForCustomerActionService].
* [Show Landing Page of "Invoice" Report For "Customer"|guide:ShowInvoiceForCustomer].

